Popular Nigerian actress, Eniola Badmus is very optimistic that Yoruba movies will be on Netflix soon enough with a proper subtitle. Gistvic Reports. Eniola Badmus said if Netflix can show Indian Movies they will definitely show Yoruba Movies someday. IS THIS POSSIBLE?? She said: “For indigenous films i think they will break someday on Netflix. But we have to do it right because Netflix will accept films that are properly done from the script to the dialogue which is very important.”